<figure class="scope-infographic" aria-labelledby="scope-infographic-title">
  <figcaption id="scope-infographic-title" class="scope-infographic-heading">
    <span class="scope-infographic-eyebrow">GHG Protocol</span>
    Emissions scopes for commercial estates
  </figcaption>
  <div class="scope-infographic-stack" role="group" aria-label="Emissions scopes pyramid">
    <article class="scope-stack-band scope-stack-band--3">
      <div class="scope-stack-band-inner">
        <span class="scope-stack-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <div class="scope-stack-copy">
          <h3>Scope 3 <span class="scope-stack-tag">Value chain</span></h3>
          <p>Emissions you influence but do not directly burn or buy — upstream and downstream of your operation.</p>
          <ul class="scope-stack-examples">
            <li>Purchased goods &amp; food supply</li>
            <li>Business travel &amp; staff commuting</li>
            <li>Waste, water &amp; tenant emissions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="scope-stack-band scope-stack-band--2 scope-stack-band--focus">
      <div class="scope-stack-band-inner">
        <span class="scope-stack-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <div class="scope-stack-copy">
          <h3>Scope 2 <span class="scope-stack-tag">Purchased energy</span></h3>
          <p>Indirect emissions from electricity, heat or steam you buy for the site.</p>
          <ul class="scope-stack-examples">
            <li>Grid electricity — lighting, HVAC, refrigeration</li>
            <li>Power quality &amp; voltage waste</li>
            <li>Sub-metered plant &amp; kitchen load</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="scope-stack-band scope-stack-band--1 scope-stack-band--focus">
      <div class="scope-stack-band-inner">
        <span class="scope-stack-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <div class="scope-stack-copy">
          <h3>Scope 1 <span class="scope-stack-tag">Direct on site</span></h3>
          <p>Emissions from sources you own or control — burned or released at the building.</p>
          <ul class="scope-stack-examples">
            <li>Gas boilers &amp; kitchen gas</li>
            <li>Refrigerant leaks from plant</li>
            <li>Company-owned vehicles</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
  <div class="scope-infographic-site" aria-hidden="true"><span>Your site / estate</span></div>
  <div class="scope-infographic-focus">
    <p class="scope-infographic-focus-label">Where Green Wing works</p>
    <p>We find and reduce <strong>Scope 1 and Scope 2 energy use</strong> on operating sites — gas, electricity and plant waste — then prove the saving with meter data your finance and sustainability teams can use.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="scope-infographic-flow" aria-label="From energy savings to carbon reporting">
    <div class="scope-flow-step"><span class="scope-flow-icon" aria-hidden="true">1</span><p><strong>Discover</strong> hidden waste on site</p></div>
    <div class="scope-flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
    <div class="scope-flow-step"><span class="scope-flow-icon" aria-hidden="true">2</span><p><strong>Reduce</strong> kWh &amp; gas consumption</p></div>
    <div class="scope-flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
    <div class="scope-flow-step"><span class="scope-flow-icon" aria-hidden="true">3</span><p><strong>Report</strong> lower Scope 1 &amp; 2</p></div>
  </div>
</figure>
